{"pin":"BH02224","subcodes":[{"code":"BH02224","anchor":"","first_line":"The Most Exalted Pen in these days speaketh in the Persian tongue, that the birds soaring in the atmosphere of divine knowledge may comprehend the utterance of the All-Merciful [3.5s]... ...Some have regarded it as lawful to infringe on the integrity of the substance of their neighbor, and have made light of the injunction of God","first_line_orig":"قلم اعلی این ایام بلسان پارسی تکلم میفرماید تا طایران هوای عرفان بیان رحمن را  ","language":"5","word_count":"400","subjects":"@theft; seizing the properties of others, @purity of heart; sincerity of intention; sanctity, @honesty; truthfulness; trustworthiness, @mission of the Manifestation of God in the world, @suffering and imprisonment, @detachment; severance; renunciation; patience","notes":" \u003ca href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20070930181707/http://bahai-library.com/resources/leiden.list/leiden.list.html#358\"\u003eLL#358\u003c/a\u003e","translations":[],"writing_refs":[{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"el","lang_name":"Greek"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"fa","lang_name":"Persian"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"te","lang_name":"Telugu"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"fr","lang_name":"French"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"hu","lang_name":"Hungarian"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"it","lang_name":"Italian"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"ja","lang_name":"Japanese"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"ko","lang_name":"Korean"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"pl","lang_name":"Polish"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"pt","lang_name":"Portuguese"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"lv","lang_name":"Latvian"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"nl","lang_name":"D